      • process

        public Result process(BasicObligation obl,
                      BasicObligationNode oblNode,
                      Abortion aborter,
                      RuntimeInformation rti)
               throws AbortionException
        Description copied from interface: Processor
        Computes the result of this processor applied on obl.
        Parameters:
        obl - - the basic obligation that should be processed
        oblNode - - the position of the basic obligation in the obligation tree
        aborter - - the aborter, that should be checked many times against timeouts/aborts, ...
        rti - - the runtime information should only be used to build new executable strategies for the result. This information can be ignored for all processors that deliver only Success or Fail as resulting strategies.
        Returns:
        the result of this processor
        Throws:
        AbortionException
